《'''行星地球2'''》（{{lang-en|'''Planet Earth II'''}}），大陆、台灣译为《'''地-{球}-脉动2'''》，香港譯為《'''天與-{地}-II'''》（[[明珠台|明珠台]]）及《'''走過森林和原野'''》（[[翡翠台|翡翠台]]），是一部[[BBC|BBC]]自然紀錄片，為2006年播出的《[[行星地球|行星地球]]》的續集<ref>{{cite news |last=Barra |first=Leo |url=http://variety.com/2016/tv/global/david-attenborough-bbc-planet-earth-ii-1201711576/ |title=David Attenborough to Narrate BBC Documentary Series 'Planet Earth II' |work=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]] |date=22 February 2016 |accessdate=24 April 2016 |archive-date=2021-02-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210220102955/https://variety.com/2016/tv/global/david-attenborough-bbc-planet-earth-ii-1201711576/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last=Hurley |first=Laura |url=http://www.cinemablend.com/television/Planet-Earth-2-Happening-Here-What-We-Know-120027.html |title=Planet Earth 2 Is Happening, Here's What We Know |work=CinemaBlend.com |date=22 February 2016 |accessdate=24 April 2016 |archive-date=2017-09-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170912192644/http://www.cinemablend.com/television/Planet-Earth-2-Happening-Here-What-We-Know-120027.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2016年10月9日BBC發佈其預告片。2016年11月6日開始于[[英国广播公司第一台|英国广播公司第一台]]（BBC One）播出<ref name=PEII2016>{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/mediacentre/latestnews/2016/planet-earth-hoppipolla|title=Sigur Rós rework Hoppipolla for the BBC's Planet Earth II trailer|publisher=BBC Media Centre|accessdate=11 October 2016|archive-date=2020-11-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201120230743/https://www.bbc.co.uk/mediacentre/latestnews/2016/planet-earth-hoppipolla|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

