==製作==
2013年BBC首次宣佈要製作這一季紀錄片，預定名字是《One Planet》（一個行星），後來改為現名<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/entertainment-arts-24207865|title=BBC commissions Blue Planet follow up|publisher=BBC News|access-date=2016-10-18|archive-date=2020-04-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200407161330/https://www.bbc.com/news/entertainment-arts-24207865|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://realscreen.com/2014/04/08/miptv-14-zdf-to-coproduce-bbc-series-one-planet/|title=MIPTV '14: ZDF to coproduce BBC series 'One Planet'|publisher=Realscreen|access-date=2016-10-18|archive-date=2019-12-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191221151040/http://realscreen.com/2014/04/08/miptv-14-zdf-to-coproduce-bbc-series-one-planet/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/mediacentre/latestnews/2016/planet-earth-two|title=Sir David Attenborough to present brand new landmark natural history series for BBC One|publisher=BBC Media Centre|access-date=2016-10-18|archive-date=2021-01-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210124170723/https://www.bbc.co.uk/mediacentre/latestnews/2016/planet-earth-two|dead-url=no}}</ref>。其預告片中的背景音樂與前作一樣，都是來自冰島歌手[[詩格洛絲|詩格洛絲]]的《Hoppípolla》<ref name=PEII2016/>。
